Here's the quick tutorial of my previous compilation video I made 100% in Adobe Premiere Pro! This is a quick breakdown of my editing workflow, where I also show you the tools that I like using the most: Speed Ramp, Masking and Lumetri tools. I also show you how I give my video more depth by adding sound effects and tweaking the music with some audio effects. I hope this tutorial gives you a little glimpse at how easy it is to create a video within Premiere Pro, and also that it makes you want to give it a try yourself!
Check out the link in my stories to check out Adobe's website and try Premiere Pro!
